story: Mohamed Abdel-Gawad shared his post to the group: Egyptian Geeks.
name: Mohamed
description:
Very Urgnent Vacancies: 
3- Android Developer - Senior 
Skills & Requirements: 
• 3+ years’ experience developing apps for android and at least 5 app in the Google Play (yours or one you worked on). 
• Intermediate to expert level skills in Java development. • Comfortable in a fast-paced, agile environment. 
• Passion and appreciation for great design and exceptional UI/UX. 
• Experience in deployment to the Google Play. 
• Intermediate skills in data structures such as XML and JSON. 
• Prototyping mobile apps. 
• Knowledge of Android’s common software design patterns. 

Send CVs to: m.gawad@ebeshara.com
